description: Go for two players Play the ancient Chinese board game against another human opponent locally. Go is a simple yet deep strategic board game thought to have been invented some 2500 years ago in China. Today the game is played by both amateurs and professionals alike world wide. igo is a simple yet powerful Go app that will allow users to play a game of Go against another player. The app is also capable of reading .sgf (Smart Game Format, a popular format in which Go games are saved) files so you can review your games or other player's games on the go on your Android device.
